text: 10:19: a Mul 20:13; Iphy 5:17; b Mul 20:14; Iphy 5:18; c Mul 20:15; Iphy 5:19; d Mul 20:16; Iphy 5:20; e Mul 20:12; Iphy 5:16 Na ne muyungthek ne thieg: bran shii ne sgoh arek rabo, chiih-è, siulao arek rabo chiih-è, mugo agow rabo; chiih-è, gai bran chiang shii biidiie akhlam rabo; chiih-è gai ro mana shii biidiie khlam ne ayie rabo Chiih-è aphuii nane amuii shii ilab rek bo.
